/* Table: base_DepotLocation */
/*==============================================================*/
create table base_DepotLocation (
locationID int identity,
DepotID int null,
LocationCode nvarchar(30) null,
IsDel bit null,
Apptime datetime null,
"IsUplocation(是否上架库位)" int null,
"IsZZ(是否临时库)" int null,
constraint PK_BASE_DEPOTLOCATION primary key (locationID)
)
